# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或者做生意嘅時候，當個價跌或者蝕到某個位，就賣出或者停止，避免蝕得更多；通常用嚟控制損失
eng:to stop loss; to cut one's losses
<eg>
yue:隻股票跌咗兩成，我決定止蝕離場。 (zek3 gu2 piu3 dit3 zo2 loeng5 sing4, ngo5 kyut3 ding6 zi2 sit6 lei4 coeng4.)
eng:The stock has dropped by 20%, so I've decided to cut my losses and exit.
<eg>
yue:做生意要識止蝕，唔好愈蝕愈做。 (zou6 saang1 ji3 jiu3 sik1 zi2 sit6, m4 hou2 jyut6 sit6 jyut6 zou6.)
eng:You have to know when to cut your losses in business; don't keep going deeper into the red.
